{"tid":1639706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議員麥康奈爾：我希望NBA可以學習香港人的勇氣和不要放棄港人珍而重之的表達自由、人權和自治","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:24:24.000Z","uid":70063,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea489eb80ca2c7349ff1bf4aeefc7516b1f483f0","tid":1639706,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:44:17.000Z","msg":"The people of Hong Kong have risked much more than money to defend their freedom of expression, human rights, and autonomy. I hope the @NBA can learn from that courage and not abandon those values for the sake of their bottom line.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1181557253075288066?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1181557253075288066%3Fs%3D09&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vkv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=845cb49b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1181557253075288066%3Fs%3D09&h=839d780f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1181557253075288066?s=09</a>"},{"pid":"040380fd4f41bb46b1d320afbc43203b574812a3","tid":1639706,"uid":57566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"Hocc:香港是站在全球維護人道抗爭的前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該要大大力宣傳 <br />\n文宣可以行美國嗰種世界警察style"},{"pid":"1918f2603c18d263aa5384ec10f4dde3351a856c","tid":1639706,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:54:04.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"2f84ee6b8793a2fdd2e49ea947430bbede9529ef","tid":1639706,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc7097a0c2c5cd4f144f358b3e81741a597d905","tid":1639706,"uid":205826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"我講你知點解宜家應該打文宣戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639321</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eeb7ed6afff483bc6b75d721d152fa967dae9ce5","tid":1639706,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}